{"tid":462942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公屋廢老扣滿分被收樓 點火自焚死唔去","createTime":"2017-11-09T04:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T09:21:13.000Z","uid":39539,"like":193,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"1c61a5fb52be8d17478d51f6d779db0c020f7d0e","tid":462942,"uid":39539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:43:26.000Z","msg":"青衣長青邨青松樓7樓一個單位，早上10時許，一名男子反鎖屋內。現場消息稱，房屋署人員上門收樓，該男住戶拒絕開門，雙方對峙一段時間，穿著頭盔和防暴裝備的警員，手持盾牌在單位門外戒備。消防員用工具打爛氣窗玻璃，裡面即爆出火球，同一時間消防員開喉射水，迅速將火種撲滅，隨後將傷者送院。警方正展開調查，暫列縱火案，拘捕涉案男子。<br />\n街坊稱，兩周前房署人員也曾上門收樓，但60餘歲的男戶主拒絕，並且情緒激動，手持打火機要脅「要收就攬住一齊死」，房署唯有暫緩行動。今日再次登門，即召警方及消防員在場戒備。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/09/124324_4c896a0d2414d4f986d39ef6d5e5a441.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F09%2F124324_4c896a0d2414d4f986d39ef6d5e5a441.jpg&h=42127e80&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ae1a675fbe406fa9f02047cf3d2d6a40adc068b","tid":462942,"uid":51904,"like":149,"dislike":4,"score":145,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:46:58.000Z","msg":"告佢縱火加收返佢間公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0f20e34e7ff1613a4a54890e9db2bb16d2a9ba5","tid":462942,"uid":108696,"like":416,"dislike":4,"score":412,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:49:24.000Z","msg":"其實佢都係想有個地方過埋最尾幾十年...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n坐監咪又有地方住 又有飯食囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f5e03a26891a65bd7795c3826a52ed06e3f205","tid":462942,"uid":39800,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:49:45.000Z","msg":"正一垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f5fce9734683fdfea934ba421567442bccfa20","tid":462942,"uid":42188,"like