faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如公屋/中轉屋住戶在<span style=\"color: red;\">兩年內</span>被扣除的分數累計達16分，其租約/暫准證將被終止。 <br />\n真 廢老"},{"pid":"39abd4f837a986d9fe8afc4c9560397e76a81a10","tid":462942,"uid":24781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T05:51:30.000Z","msg":"啲廢中係度搞亂檔<br />\n又唔撚去睇精神科醫生"},{"pid":"5d83777036d959429d3deba78a4e7e051fb8e64a","tid":462942,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T05:53:56.000Z","msg":"廢老"},{"pid":"2cf08a0b3dcf89aaac1f622f387147ed132d6edc","tid":462942,"uid":57307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T05:59:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">前人教落: 公屋 , 公綜 , 殘津 , 白卡<br />\n人稱4大天王</span>"},{"pid":"ce83d4dc2ca4f42367bf28c32ef98cd89d14dbe8","tid":462942,"uid":84869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:00:45.000Z","msg":"公屋的規則好多人都犯<br />\n但如果你唔係好過份<br />\n房署好少真係會去到扣你分<br />\n<br />\n要做到扣晒你全部分收屋 證明你真係仆街得好緊要<br />\n<br />\n所以只能講句抵死"},{"pid":"46c7d1b0892fdb1841faf8df1adee258bda5cf43","tid":462942,"uid":112627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:03:01.000Z","msg":"唔死去坐監lo<br />\n咁咪唔怕冇屋企"},{"pid":"e863d5a29503f2b14055dc72c143faa33b3af4a3","tid":462942,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:11:04.000Z","msg":"隔離左右真係多得佢唔少<br />\n成間屋都俾佢熏黑晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cd08997b7f89c748cb53585dfdf84643c65dc08","tid":462942,"uid":39539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:43:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隔離左右真係多得佢唔少<br />\n成間屋都俾佢熏黑晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收屋跟住中轉屋，廢老2年又上樓，到時又自焚又中轉屋又上公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d296374efafaf2fe59b0f2560bb18358a87a917","tid":462942,"uid":57633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:47:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>隔離左右真係多得佢唔少<br />\n成間屋都俾佢熏黑晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收屋跟住中轉屋，廢老2年又上樓，到時又自焚又中轉屋又上公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n由 2006 年 1 月 1 日起，因違反扣分制或其他租約條款而被房委會終止租約的<br />\n前住戶，他們在租約被終止後的兩年內，不得透過公屋輪候冊申請公屋。房<br />\n委會亦不會把質素較佳的單位(以地理位置、樓齡和樓層而言)編配予他們。"},{"pid":"a48ee387adf79c2d338664198ec75964ce06a976","tid":462942,"uid":91685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:55:22.000Z","msg":"咁都扣得滿就抵佢死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快d搬走咪撚害人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed9cb37594d387674ee929fe9258c2debc1fe55","tid":462942,"uid":41198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T07:08:16.000Z","msg":"當傻人發現案 掟佢入青山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時慘撚過死"},{"pid":"fdaf3c2aa9eb6c8dcadd1eb07697afc60a7ac8a2","tid":462942,"uid":36363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T07:12:26.000Z","msg":"公屋扣分已經hea到爆，都可以扣滿 世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4046368fed219ce11d590558f132523ce2ab48e4","tid":462942,"uid":26976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T07:28:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>衡仔又可以出動啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n縱火KOL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4901654be2a60edf29ed7720bb88001386baedcf","tid":462942,"uid":156085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T07:28:24.000Z","msg":"今次燒佢唔死，下次又害鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda476178df74a39c518a8f7c1c75354c60fdb4a","tid":462942,"uid":39539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T07:30:57.000Z","msg